Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

BREAKING: stream=True with tools no longer raises ValueError.

llm_request_builder.py: removed fail-closed block for stream+tools
llm_stream_normalizer.py: tool call delta reconstruction
  - OpenAI: choices[0].delta.tool_calls → reconstructed function calls
  - Anthropic: content_block_start/delta → reconstructed tool_use blocks
  - Arguments concatenated from deltas → parsed JSON

7 new tests (tool reconstruction: OpenAI single/multi, Anthropic, empty, text-only)
Updated 2 existing tests (ValueError → allowed)

386 tests total passing.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
